The experiment of UV-C elicitation was performed using 4 weeks grown calli by following the protocol of Anjum et al.29. The UV-C radiations were applied on cultures at distance of 15 cm from Ultraviolet-C lamp (254 nm, Model ZQJ-254, China with value (intensity) of 3 W/m2). The experimental Ultraviolet-C treatments (kJ/m2) were calculated as;\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
